Subject: Recently upgraded and some reports not working
Description:
We recently upgraded and now have some reports that display data but we cannot download the data. (File not found error).

Trying to go in to the report configuration we receive the following error.

Unable to log error to SA: Object doesnt support porperty or method 'LogJSMessage'.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
Some users could not download reports


Resolution
By setting the report grid to interactive users were able to achieve the required outcome.
Account_Name__c: Federal Home Loan Bank of Pittsburgh
